00:23:45,040 --> 00:23:46,440
Why are you staring at me?

586
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,500
Aren't you also a mother of three?

587
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:50,640
This is our shared responsibility.

588
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:51,370
I'm leaving.

589
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,400
What's wrong with looking at you?

590
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,600
What's your problem?

591
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,360
Who told you to hang this here?

592
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:00,160
It doesn't match at all.

593
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:02,090
If not here, where should I hang it?

594
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:03,360
Like this.

595
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:07,740
You hung up and called back again.

596
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,400
Cui Guoming.

597
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:29,880
Cui Guoming.

598
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,200
Yang Fei.

599
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:35,120
Yes.

600
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:36,220
Wang Xiaojuan.

601
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:38,440
What a coincidence.

602
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:40,280
We haven't seen each other since high school graduation.

603
00:24:40,280 --> 00:24:42,040
Didn't you get into the Engineering University?

604
00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:42,970
Top of the class.

605
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:44,760
No, no. I was second in the class.

606
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:46,690
Well, second is still impressive.

607
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:49,560
How did you end up selling clothes here?

608
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:51,320
Well, you see,

609
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,600
it's my wife's shop.

610
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:55,000
I'm just helping her out.

611
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,040
I was thinking,

612
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,840
how could a top student like you

613
00:24:58,840 --> 00:25:00,900
end up selling clothes on the street.

614
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:02,920
Isn't selling clothes pretty good?

615
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,720
Getting to experience fashion.

616
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,480
So what do you do now?

617
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,720
I'm still in mechanical engineering.

618
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:11,520
Isn't that what I've been doing since graduation?

619
00:25:12,320 --> 00:25:13,680
You're still doing well.

620
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,960
We saw you on TV

621
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,040
last year.

622
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,120
You still sing so well.

623
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,200
Really good.

624
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:21,290
You're good at whatever you do.

625
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,480
Unlike us two.

626
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,360
We didn't get into college

627
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:25,400
and can't do anything special.

628
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,320
We're now partners,

629
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,360
running a fur coat shop

630
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:28,400
on Jiudao Street.

631
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,120
Why don't you bring your wife

632
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:30,960
to our shop sometime?

633
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,200
Sure.

634
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,120
So your fur coats...

635
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:35,680
Look at you, you can only wear fur coats.

636
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,440
I have everything else here.

637
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,040
Feel free to look around.

638
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:39,600
And afterward,

639
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:40,640
take whatever you like.

640
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,640
It'll be my treat.

641
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,840
No need.

642
00:25:43,600 --> 00:25:45,060
We can still afford these.

643
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:45,880
Take a look.

644
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:46,880
If you like it, take it.

645
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:47,840
Be happy!

646
00:25:49,120 --> 00:25:50,850
The style is quite innovative.

647
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,680
It seems

648
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,080
pretty good.

649
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:56,960
Not bad.

650
00:25:57,320 --> 00:25:58,680
Sergei.

651
00:25:58,960 --> 00:25:59,800
Who?

652
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:06,120
Why are you selling second-hand goods?

653
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,680
Well,

654
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,440
we're doing business.

655
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:11,120
Making money is all that matters, right?

656
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:11,880
That's true.

657
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:14,200
So then.

658
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,290
It's been disinfected.

659
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,200
Actually,

660
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:20,080
it looks pretty nice anyway.

661
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:20,720
How about this,

662
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:21,840
when you have time, let's

663
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:22,680
get together sometime.

664
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,640
Sure.

665
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,400
Alright, bye then.

666
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:31,010
Come by anytime.

667
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,680
Okay, bye.

668
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:34,960
Good.

669
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:15,400
Come here and stand still.

670
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,640
Didn't I tell you

671
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,880
to remove all these laundry tags?

672
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:23,690
Why didn't you remove them?

673
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,120
I was only responsible for half of them.

674
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,920
The other half was Er Pang's job.

675
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:35,490
Mom said we're not buying a Xiali car anymore.

676
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,240
We can't afford it right now.

677
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,640
Our first priority is to get a villa.

678
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,640
We need to move into a bigger house.

679
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,960
After that, I can buy you a Santana.

680
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:46,360
Okay.

681
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:47,840
It's fine that we don't have a Xiali now.

682
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:48,960
Or a Santana.

683
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,160
None of that matters.

684
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:50,920
But

685
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:51,880
I just need you to pay for

686
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,280
the cost of one Santana tire.

687
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,720
That would make me happy.

688
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:56,580
What do you want to buy?

689
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,320
I want a bicycle with gears.

690
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,920
Everyone in my class has one.

691
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,560
What's a bicycle with gears?

692
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:05,680
This is it.

693
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,160
A multi-speed bicycle.

694
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,880
So it's controlled by gears

695
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,040
that regulate

696
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:38,400
the speed changes, right?

697
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:43,440
What's the highest

698
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:45,980
gear available on the market now?

699
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:47,560
Eight.

700
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:52,400
This thing is a real money-maker.

701
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:54,640
Dad,

702
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:56,580
what are you planning now?

703
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:58,960
What do you mean?

704
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:00,600
You're not thinking of selling

705
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,730
multi-speed bicycles again, are you?

706
00:29:03,120 --> 00:29:04,980
What am I supposed to do with this?

707
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:18,960
It's from the Justice Department.

708
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:21,320
They're temporarily suspending your lawyer's license.

709
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:22,360
Once the issue with the pinhole glasses

710
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:23,360
is cleared up.

711
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:24,890
We'll see about that later.

712
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,080
Aren't you even going to look at it?

713
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:30,940
I already knew this would happen.

714
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:31,960
My license is suspended.

715
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,560
What's the point of looking?

716
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,880
Our boutique store

717
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,210
is doing quite well now.

718
00:29:37,280 --> 00:29:38,880
You don't have to be a lawyer.

719
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:41,960
What, does being a lawyer pay better than this?

720
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:44,960
You're right.

721
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,480
But I feel like selling clothes

722
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:51,920
gives me a sense of wasting my talents.

723
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:53,560
You've enjoyed a few peaceful days

724
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,760
and now you want to stir things up again?

725
00:29:56,320 --> 00:29:58,200
I've been thinking

726
00:29:59,560 --> 00:30:01,160
if I could do something

727
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,560
with better prospects.

728
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:06,840
What do you want to do?

729
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:08,680
Don't worry.

730
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:10,400
I just want

731
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:12,130
to go back to my old profession,

732
00:30:12,560 --> 00:30:13,220
mechanics.

733
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,640
This I can support.

734
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:18,640
Is there a factory

735
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,840
offering you a high salary?

736
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:20,920
Nobody's hiring me.

737
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,650
I want to start my own business.

738
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,560
What do you want to do?

739
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:26,320
Sell multi-speed bicycles.

740
00:30:26,320 --> 00:30:26,920
What?

741
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,320
Just hear me out.

742
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,400
It doesn't cost much.

743
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:31,960
The cost is almost zero.

744
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,280
The market is full of

745
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:34,720
six-speed and eight-speed bikes.

746
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:35,880
I want to develop

747
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:38,080
twelve-speed and sixteen-speed ones.

748
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:38,920
With my skills,

749
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,920
I don't think it would be difficult.

750
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,040
Then I'll apply for a patent.

751
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:41,880
This patent,

752
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,120
once approved,

753
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:45,450
will support our family for generations.

754
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:47,120
It's quick money.

755
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,880
Didn't we want to buy a house?

756
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:49,810
If I work on this,

757
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:50,800
in just a few months we

758
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:52,000
could buy that house.

759
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:54,880
Does it really not cost anything?

760
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:55,680
Really doesn't.

761
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,960
Just give me 10,000.

762
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,440
I need to do some research,

763
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,440
buy some parts,

764
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,480
and start tinkering first.

765
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,880
If I don't make any money,

766
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,900
I won't ask you for another penny.

767
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:06,930
Alright.

768
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:10,480
I won't be at the shop much anymore.

769
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:12,940
I need to focus on research and development.

770
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:15,810
That's fine.

771
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,600
But for the monthly supply trips to Guangdong,

772
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,480
you must go.

773
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,200
We need to restock the day after tomorrow.

774
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,200
Okay, no problem.

775
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,440
Look at you.

776
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:24,960
When you were employed,

777
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,120
you were always late and left early.

778
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,780
Now that you've been laid off,

779
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:28,560
suddenly you remember

780
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,760
how good your job was.

781
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:32,640
Come here.

782
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:41,400
I've been working at the factory since college graduation,

783
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,280
for 15 years.

784
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:44,280
Because of me, our factory

785
00:31:44,560 --> 00:31:45,690
has never shut down,

786
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,480
not even once,

787
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:49,800
not for a minute, right?

788
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:50,960
That's true.

789
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,940
Hailong told me the other day.

790
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:55,080
In just these three months,

791
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,920
our factory has stopped production

792
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,800
four times due to mechanical failures.

793
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,530
It's still shut down right now.

794
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,720
The reason I seem so careless

795
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:04,360
is because of these monstrous machines.

796
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:05,400
For me,

797
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,610
it's just like Mengmeng's doll

798
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,240
or Erpang's slingshot.

799
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,960
I just love tinkering with it.

800
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:17,040
I knew you could do it.

801
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:18,320
Let's eat.

802
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:20,600
What about

803
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:23,000
the bunk beds? Are they ready?

804
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:25,400
Xiaoxue

805
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,960
will be discharged from the hospital soon.

806
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,360
Is that my job?

807
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,960
I'm just talking to myself.

808
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:33,800
I'll do it.

809
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:35,760
What are we eating?

810
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:36,960
Sauerkraut noodles.

811
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,770
Go get some chopsticks.

812
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,800
This one

813
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,980
let me borrow it later.

814
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:51,960
Sure.

815
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,360
You bought it for me anyway.

816
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:54,960
Do whatever you want with it.

817
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:57,250
You're quite generous.

818
00:32:58,080 --> 00:32:59,340
I want to take it apart.

819
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,000
Uncle, you must want to study it.

820
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,760
Yes, study it,

821
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:04,960
imitate it,

822
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:06,520
surpass it.

823
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:09,570
Uncle, you'll definitely surpass it.

824
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:13,900
Do you know about luxury cars?

825
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,340
I've heard of them.

826
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,720
Do you know why

827
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:19,380
luxury cars are so expensive?

828
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,880
It's because every part

829
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,400
is handcrafted.

830
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:23,520
In the future,

831
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:25,440
you will have your very own

832
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:27,560
handcrafted multi-speed bicycle.

833
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:29,400
An incomparable

834
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:30,960
chariot.

835
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:32,400
Priceless.

836
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:34,770
No need for such formality.

837
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,940
What are you doing?

838
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:41,160
(Russian) I have other work to do.

839
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:44,130
(Russian) I must return to St. Petersburg today.

840
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:48,720
(Russian) Besides, I cannot complete this job.

841
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:51,690
(Russian) Although I'm a mechanical expert,

842
00:33:51,800 --> 00:33:54,460
(Russian) I don't know much about this machine.

843
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:59,760
(Russian) I remember coming here for maintenance a few years ago

844
00:34:00,600 --> 00:34:03,840
(Russian) and meeting a young man named Cui.

845
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:07,050
(Russian) His skill level is very high

846
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:09,480
(Russian) and he knows enough about the machine.

847
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,739
(Russian) Where is he?

848
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:14,570
Director, I'll translate for you in a moment.

849
00:34:15,080 --> 00:34:15,940
(Russian) Who?

850
00:34:16,159 --> 00:34:18,600
(Russian) Cui. Yes, that's right, Cui.

851
00:34:19,199 --> 00:34:21,639
(Russian) He can definitely do it.

852
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:26,080
(Russian) I've already done my part.

853
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,800
[Speaking Russian] Goodbye.

854
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:29,460
[Speaking Russian] Goodbye.

855
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,440
If I'm not mistaken,

856
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:46,179
he was talking about Cui Guoming.

857
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:48,159
I think so.

858
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,920
Now that the butcher is gone,

859
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:56,050
we're stuck with the hairy pig.

860
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:57,680
It's not that bad.

861
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:58,600
Not that bad?

862
00:34:58,600 --> 00:34:59,360
Really?

863
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:01,410
We've been shut down for 7 days.

864
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,680
So what do you suggest?

865
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,880
Find him.

866
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,080
Pay him if necessary.

867
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:06,880
Director,

868
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,000
given our relationship,

869
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,260
how can I approach him?

870
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,860
You want me to find him?

871
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,040
I have an idea.

872
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,320
But you...

873
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,300
need to cooperate with me.

874
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,320
Hailong, Liu Ye,

875
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,920
the director wants to see you both.

876
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:29,680
Hurry up.

877
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,320
We've been shut down for 7 days.

878
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,000
It's urgent.

879
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:31,960
Hurry!

880
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:33,920
We're trying to solve the problem,

881
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:34,520
aren't we?

882
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:48,960
Because of

883
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:52,440
mechanical failure, we can't deliver on time.

884
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,640
To the outside world,

885
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:55,840
I am the primary person responsible.

886
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:57,120
But internally,

887
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,440
you two

888
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,760
are definitely the first

889
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,120
and second responsible parties.

890
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:02,840
Right?

891
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:05,280
Currently our factory's

892
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,840
performance is extremely poor.

893
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,840
If this shipment

894
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,240
isn't delivered on time,

895
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:11,320
we're definitely finished.

896
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:13,200
Our second round of layoffs

897
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,240
affects 1,500 people.

898
00:36:16,800 --> 00:36:18,120
If that happens,

899
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:20,840
then our second round of layoffs

900
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:24,040
will be 1,502 people.

901
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,730
Are you two laid off too?

902
00:36:35,200 --> 00:36:36,840
Before 3 PM today,

903
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,720
you must fix it.

904
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:40,620
No matter what methods you use

905
00:36:40,680 --> 00:36:42,680
or who you find to help,

906
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,380
Do you understand?

907
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,360
Director.

908
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:50,240
We've both been working very hard.

909
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:51,440
Really.

910
00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:53,840
We can't fix it in such a short time.

911
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:55,880
That machine is too old.

912
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:57,000
What did I just say?

913
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,680
Did you two hear me?

914
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,640
This is a military order.

915
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:01,980
Let me say it again.

916
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:03,800
No matter what methods you use,

917
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:04,840
no matter who

918
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,960
you find to help.

919
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:08,940
Do you understand?

920
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:13,840
Director,

921
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:16,280
I think I understand now.

922
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,760
We'll do our best.

923
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,900
Not just your best.

924
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:21,160
It's mandatory.

925
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:25,050
Quick, get some tissue for him.

926
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:26,440
He's bleeding.

927
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,880
Go to the infirmary quickly.

928
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,340
Get it checked out. Hurry.

929
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:33,680
We'll go after lunch.

930
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,170
Who are you looking for?

931
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:36,580
You know, that person.

932
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:51,040
Take this over there too.

933
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:54,960
Sister-in-law,

934
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:55,360
Sister-in-law,

935
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,090
you're here.

936
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,160
What perfect timing!

937
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:57,840
I've just prepared

938
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,160
two pieces of clothing for you both.

939
00:37:59,160 --> 00:38:00,120
Take them with you later.

940
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:01,520
Sure. That's kind of you.

941
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,600
What's up, brother?

942
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,930
What happened to your face?

943
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,060
My wife didn't come home until 6 AM

944
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:13,440
so I asked her what she was doing last night.

945
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,500
She got upset and started hitting me.

946
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,320
Why did it turn violent?

947
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,800
How badly did you hurt her?

948
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:21,300
I would never lay a hand on her.

949
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,840
She scratched me.

950
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:25,320
Maybe I should go talk to her.

951
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:27,120
She could just explain herself.

952
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:28,400
Why get physical?

953
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,720
Brother.

954
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,490
We came to see you today.

955
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,800
Not about this issue.

956
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,760
Coming home at 6 in the morning

957
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:37,890
and getting violent - that's serious.

958
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:39,440
Brother, my problem

959
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,520
can wait a few days.

960
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:43,120
We're here today for something more important.

961
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,320
What's so important?

962
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,000
The factory machine broke down.

963
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,720
We've been shut down for 7 days.

964
00:38:47,720 --> 00:38:48,920
If we can't fix it,

965
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:51,330
we won't be able to deliver our orders.

966
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,920
Why are you telling me this?

967
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,360
We want to ask for your help.

968
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,880
Please come back and fix the machine.

969
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,840
We really can't fix it ourselves.

970
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,760
I can't help.

971
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,320
I'm going to pick up goods with your sister-in-law tonight.

972
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:00,040
I still need to.

973
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:00,920
Brother, please go.

974
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,720
I won't go. I'll go.

975
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:03,440
What would I do there?

976
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,400
I've been laid off already.

977
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,480
You've been laid off.

978
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,440
But the two of us haven't yet.

979
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:08,240
I won't go.

980
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:13,760
Mr. Cui.

981
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,880
The factory manager made an announcement today.

982
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,600
He said if we don't fix the machine today,

983
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:20,000
we'll both be kicked out,

984
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,580
laid off immediately.

985
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:23,640
So what about me?

986
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:24,320
If I lose my job,

987
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,850
what will happen to my wife?

988
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,920
Please help me one more time.

989
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:29,850
I'm begging you.

990
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,160
Let's go.

991
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,720
Take your clothes. Here.

992
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,720
Don't rush.

993
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:42,250
Thank you, sister-in-law.

994
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:22,720
Thanks.

995
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:45,360
Director,

996
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,320
you're so wise!

997
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:03,520
Let's go, Director.

998
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:21,400
Guess if I fixed the machine?

999
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:23,800
Go home and change your clothes quickly.

1000
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:26,080
Aren't you going to the train station later?

1001
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:26,880
I'm leaving.

1002
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:29,720
Xiaoxue will be discharged tonight.

1003
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:30,480
Don't forget to pick her up.

1004
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:31,680
I got it. Let's go.

1005
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,520
Hello?

1006
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:00,240
It's me, Hailong.

1007
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:01,440
I'm in Guangdong.

1008
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:03,400
What's wrong? Is the machine broken again?

1009
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,800
The machine isn't broken.

1010
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:06,120
Xiaomei has left.

1011
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:08,740
Where could she have gone?

1012
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,800
Yesterday when I got home,

1013
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:12,600
I found a letter she left me.

1014
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:15,780
She said she never wants to see this loser again.

1015
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,040
She's gone.

1016
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:19,120
She'll never let me see her again.

1017
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,200
You two have Xiaozhi now.

1018
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:21,440
Where could she possibly go?

1019
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:22,800
She's really gone.

1020
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:24,840
I love her,

1021
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:27,360
even though she doesn't love me.

1022
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:29,760
Isn't it better that she's gone?

1023
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:30,320
You can find someone else.

1024
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,450
She doesn't want me.

1025
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:33,160
She doesn't want Xiaozhi either.

1026
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:33,560
Enough.

1027
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,840
Can't you act like a man?

1028
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,760
Don't be like this.

1029
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:36,520
Hey.

1030
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:37,680
I'm watching the game.
